<h4><strong>Why should I join PRSM?</strong></h4><p style="text-align: left;">PRSM Association is the leading membership organization for retail and multi-site facilities and supplier professionals. PRSM empowers the facilities management professionals with best practices, benchmarking, education, discussion forums and trusted partnerships. <a href="/Portals/27/Membership/Reports/1.2019 - Retailer Semi-Annual Report - Store _ Industry Category.pdf">Download the 2019 Retailer Semi-Annual Report</a></p><p><table align="center" style="width: 0px;"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=""><a class="btn btn-lg btn-info text-center" style="color: black;" href="/Membership/Retailer-Membership">MULTI-SITE/RETAILER</a>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;<a class="btn btn-lg btn-info text-center" style="color: black;" href="/Membership/Supplier-Membership">SUPPLIER</a></td></tr></tbody></table></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
